1, Azure Data factory - ADF
2, Azure Databricks


ADF:
Datapipeline without using Spark or any distributed processing engine for ETL / ELT
Source to Target
our example: Moving Azure storage data to SQL DB and then making dashboards in PowerBI

Databricks:
Instead of creating our Spark cluster and writing default code to read and write the data, This Databricks notebook automatically giving to us.
NO need to worry about Spark infrastructure, monitoring and all
